### Bandit Captain
Always searching for a chance to use their freshly sharpened blade, the captains and leaders of bandit communities need to be particularly ruthless and cunning, or risk their own purses being cut, along with their throats.

### Berserker
Particularly common among trolls is the sight of a terrifying warrior so lost in a haze of pure violence that they do not seem to register any pain at all, simply powering through until everything is dead. 


___
> ## Bandit Captain <!-- https://wc5e-cr-calculator.frogvall.com/?0;15;45;5;13;18;0;18;0;18;0;0;0;0;0;0;0;;;;1;2;;;;;;;;;;1;;;;1;;;;10;;;;;;;;;;; -->
>*Medium humanoid (any race), any non-lawful alignment*
> ___
> - **Armor Class** 15 (studded leather)
> - **Hit Points** 45 (7d8 + 14)
> - **Speed** 30 ft.
>___
> |  STR  |  DEX  |  CON  |  INT  |  WIS  |  CHA  |
> |:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|
